ids_alerts.rule_msg: POLICY-OTHER HTTP request by IPv4 address attempt
ids_alerts.rule_raw: alert tcp any any -> any $HTTP_PORTS ( msg:"POLICY-OTHER HTTP request by IPv4 address attempt"; flow:to_server,established; http_header; content:"Host:",fast_pattern,nocase; pcre:"/^Host\x3a\s*(?:(?:25[0-5]|2[0-4][0-9]|[01]?[0-9]?[0-9])\.){3}(?:25[0-5]|2[0-4][0-9]|[01]?[0-9]?[0-9])\s*:?\s*\d*\s*$/ims"; service:http; reference:url,www.w3.org/Protocols/rfc2616/rfc2616-sec15.html; classtype:policy-violation; sid:50447; rev:1; )

ids_alerts.rule_msg: (http_inspect) backslash character appears in the path portion of a URI
ids_alerts.rule_raw: alert ( gid:119; sid:9; rev:3; msg:"(http_inspect) backslash character appears in the path portion of a URI"; metadata: rule-type preproc; service:http; classtype:not-suspicious;)

ids_alerts.rule_msg: PROTOCOL-DNS squid proxy dns PTR record response denial of service attempt
ids_alerts.rule_raw: alert udp $EXTERNAL_NET 53 -> $HOME_NET any ( msg:"PROTOCOL-DNS squid proxy dns PTR record response denial of service attempt"; flow:to_client; content:"|00 0C 00 01|"; content:"|00 0C 00 01|",within 4,distance 2; content:"|00 01 00|",within 3,distance 4; metadata:policy max-detect-ips drop; service:dns; reference:bugtraq,12551; reference:cve,2005-0446; classtype:attempted-dos; sid:17484; rev:10; )

ids_alerts.rule_msg: ET MALWARE Laplas Clipper - Regex CnC Request
ids_alerts.rule_raw: alert http $HOME_NET any -> $EXTERNAL_NET any (msg:"ET MALWARE Laplas Clipper - Regex CnC Request"; flow:established,to_server; http.method; content:"GET"; http.uri; content:"/bot/regex"; startswith; fast_pattern; reference:url,blog.cyble.com/2022/11/02/new-laplas-clipper-distributed-by-smokeloader/; classtype:trojan-activity; sid:2039775; rev:2; metadata:affected_product Windows_XP_Vista_7_8_10_Server_32_64_Bit, attack_target Client_Endpoint, created_at 2022_11_14, deployment Perimeter, former_category MALWARE, performance_impact Low, confidence High, signature_severity Major, updated_at 2023_02_16;)

ids_alerts.rule_msg: ET USER_AGENTS Go HTTP Client User-Agent
ids_alerts.rule_raw: alert http $HOME_NET any -> $EXTERNAL_NET any (msg:"ET USER_AGENTS Go HTTP Client User-Agent"; flow:established,to_server; http.user_agent; content:"Go-http-client"; nocase; fast_pattern; classtype:misc-activity; sid:2024897; rev:2; metadata:attack_target Client_Endpoint, created_at 2017_10_23, deployment Perimeter, former_category USER_AGENTS, signature_severity Major, updated_at 2020_08_13;)

ids_alerts.rule_msg: ET MALWARE Laplas Clipper - SetOnline CnC Checkin
ids_alerts.rule_raw: alert http $HOME_NET any -> $EXTERNAL_NET any (msg:"ET MALWARE Laplas Clipper - SetOnline CnC Checkin"; flow:established,to_server; http.method; content:"GET"; http.uri; content:"/bot/online?"; startswith; fast_pattern; content:"guid="; content:"key="; pcre:"/^[a-f0-9]{64}/UR"; reference:url,blog.cyble.com/2022/11/02/new-laplas-clipper-distributed-by-smokeloader/; classtype:trojan-activity; sid:2039776; rev:2; metadata:affected_product Windows_XP_Vista_7_8_10_Server_32_64_Bit, attack_target Client_Endpoint, created_at 2022_11_14, deployment Perimeter, former_category MALWARE, performance_impact Low, confidence High, signature_severity Major, updated_at 2023_02_16;)

ids_alerts.rule_raw: alert http $HOME_NET any -> $EXTERNAL_NET any (msg:"ET MALWARE Laplas Clipper - SetOnline CnC Checkin"; flow:established,to_server; http.method; content:"GET"; http.uri; content:"/bot/online?"; startswith; fast_pattern; content:"guid="; content:"key="; pcre:"/^[a-f0-9]{64}/UR"; reference:url,blog.cyble.com/2022/11/02/new-laplas-clipper-distributed-by-smokeloader/; classtype:trojan-activity; sid:2039776; rev:2; metadata:affected_product Windows_XP_Vista_7_8_10_Server_32_64_Bit, attack_target Client_Endpoint, created_at 2022_11_14, deployment Perimeter, former_category MALWARE, performance_impact Low, confidence High, signature_severity Major, updated_at 2023_02_16;)
